description: the program finds the duplicates alright. but there seems to be no way to delete/move duplicates once you've found them. There are no buttons, no help, nothing can be found on the web... Help! It's a shame because the the program does find the duplicates
summary: it finds the duplicates, but then what?

description: it will find the duplicates but offers no option on what to do with them. no instructions on how to use it although its not in the slightest complicated. great start at a great program though

The apps does good at finding duplicate images and fast but as the other reviewers have stated there is no way to remove them. There is a trash can at the top but it won't enable. The bottom of the picture does tell where it is and the name so at least you can find it. Maybe it is just not done yet. I have found more often than not the things in the snap store don't work. Just an observation.
summary: Too bad I can't do half stars

description: nachdem dupliseek ca. 1800 Duplikate in meinen Bildern gefunden hat, friert das System fast ein. Prozessor Auslastung fast 100%, RAM Auslastung 100%, Auslagerungsdatei 100%, und dann steht fast alles.

Funktioniert für mich. Während des Hashing ist die Anwendung nicht responsiv daher nur 4 Sterne. System bietet dann an die Anwendung zu beenden oder zu warten. Beim warten läuft das Hashing einwandfrei durch.

everything works ok but when you want to delete the duplicate file the option "Put in the trash" dosnt works .

Todo bien, pero la opción para borrar los archivos en el basurero no funciona.
